title: Lebanon Money Supply M3
description: Money Supply M3 in Lebanon increased to 208725 LBP Billion in September from 192515 LBP Billion in August of 2022. Money Supply M3 in Lebanon averaged 74587.07 LBP Billion from 1975 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 213088 LBP Billion in September of 2018 and a record low of 10.65 LBP Billion in December of 1975. Lebanon Money Supply M3 includes M2 plus long-term time deposits in banks. This page provides - Lebanon Money Supply M3 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Banque Du Liban
